 <br/><a name='toc_1'></a>
<h1 class='doclevel'>1.Test Suite : lgir3552_BBT</h1>
<div><p>Test Suite pentru functionalitatea de adaugare produs</p>
</div><a name="toc_tc29092"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P232-9: AddProductTC-ECP-valid&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">lgir3552</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Test case 1 pentru ECP. Adaugarea unui produs cu o clasa valida.</p>

<p>Ne asteptam ca in urma apelarii functiei de save produsul sa fie salvat cu succes si sa apara in fisierul de persistenta</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>id -&gt; numar intreg, 0-1000<br />
nume -&gt; string, 3-32caractere<br />
pret -&gt; numar real, 2-20</p>

<p>categorie -&gt; sa fie un enum&nbsp;CategorieBautura (CLASSIC_COFFEE, MILK_COFFEE, SPECIAL_COFFEE, ICED_COFFEE, TEA,BUBBLE_TEA, JUICE, SMOOTHIE, ALL)</p>

<p>tip -&gt; sa fie un enum TipBautura(BASIC, DAIRY, LACTOSE_FREE, WATER_BASED, PLANT_BASED, POWDER, ALL)</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >ProductTest</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >addProduct_shouldSave</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">lgir3552_F01:  AdaugareProdus [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc29094"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P232-10: AddProductTC-ECP-invalid&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">lgir3552</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Test case 2 pentru ECP. Adaugarea unui produs cu o clasa invalida.</p>

<p>Ne asteptam ca in urma apelarii functiei de save produsul sa nu poata fi salvat si sa fie aruncata o exceptie</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>Datele produsului nu sunt conforme cu domeniul de definitie (ex: fara nume, pret negativ, id negativ, id duplicat)</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >ProductTest</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >addProduct_shouldThrowException</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">lgir3552_F01:  AdaugareProdus [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc29099"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P232-11: AddProductTC-BVA-valid&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">lgir3552</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Test case 3 pentru BVA valid. Adaugarea unui produs cu parametrii la limite inferioare/superioare</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>Ne asteptam ca produsul sa fie salvat cu succes si sa persiste in fisier.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>id -&gt; numar intreg, 0-1000<br />
nume -&gt; string, 3-32caractere<br />
pret -&gt; numar real, 2-20</p>

<p>tip -&gt; sa fie un enum TipBautura(BASIC, DAIRY, LACTOSE_FREE, WATER_BASED, PLANT_BASED, POWDER, ALL)</p>

<p>categorie -&gt; sa fie un enum&nbsp;CategorieBautura (CLASSIC_COFFEE, MILK_COFFEE, SPECIAL_COFFEE, ICED_COFFEE, TEA,BUBBLE_TEA, JUICE, SMOOTHIE, ALL)</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >ProductTest</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >addProduct_atBoundary_shouldSave</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">lgir3552_F01:  AdaugareProdus [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc29105"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P232-12: AddProductTC-BVA-invalid&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">lgir3552</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Test case 4 pentru BVA invalid. Adaugarea unui produs cu parametrii peste una&nbsp;din&nbsp;limitele inferioare/superioare</p>

<p>Ne asteptam ca produsul sa nu fie salvat si sa fie aruncata o exceptie.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>id -&gt; numar intreg, &lt;0 sau &gt; 1000<br />
nume -&gt; string, de dimensiune &lt; 3 sau &gt; 32<br />
pret -&gt; numar real, &lt; 2 sau &gt; 20</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >ProductTest</td></tr>
